OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FDomestic abuse charity Refuge welcomed
OL,7,Fthe announcement, but said there was
OL,8,Fstill a "staggering" funding gap for
OL,9,Fservices, including refuges.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Victim Support said CPS
OL,12,Fstaff taking part in the pilot needed
OL,13,Fto have specialist training.
OL,15,FThe scheme will mean victims of crime
OL,16,Fwill be able to meet prosecutors ahead
OL,17,Fof crown court trials. It is hoped
OL,18,Fthis means victims will be able to ask
OL,19,Fquestions about the court process.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FThere will also be more domestic abuse
OL,7,Fvictim liaison officers.
OL,9,FThe pilots will run in three areas;
OL,10,FYorkshire and Humber, Merseyside and
OL,11,FCheshire, and a region covering
OL,12,FWiltshire, Hampshire, Dorset and the
OL,13,FIsle of Wight.
OL,15,FSpeaking in the House of Commons, Ms
OL,16,FReeves said the changes would mean
OL,17,Fvictims' "voices are heard" and would
OL,18,Fhelp prevent them dropping out of
OL,19,Fcourt cases.
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FShe continued: "This offer is already
OL,7,Favailable to victims of rape and
OL,8,Fserious sexual assault across the
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,F"I know from speaking with prosecutors
OL,12,Fand victims the difference these
OL,13,Fmeetings can make, and I'm pleased to
OL,14,Fsee it extended to victims of domestic
OL,15,Fabuse."
OL,26,@nD@POUsD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
