CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FLabour MP for Congleton Sarah Russell,
OL,7,Fwho asked about increasing prosecution
OL,8,Frates for violence against women and
OL,9,Fgirls, said: "I very much welcome that
OL,10,Fnews. The prosecution rates for cases
OL,11,Finvolving violence against women and
OL,12,Fgirls are shamefully low.
OL,14,F"I strongly welcome the Government's
OL,15,Fambition to tackle violence against
OL,16,Fwomen and girls."
OL,26,@qD@NOUvD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FRefuge's public affairs lead, Alice
OL,7,FRussell-Harris, said the #5 million
OL,8,Fpackage must be accompanied by
OL,9,Fincreases for "specialist domestic
OL,10,Fabuse services".
OL,12,FMs Russell-Harris said: "Refuge
OL,13,Fwelcomes today's announcement of an
OL,14,Fadditional #5 million for the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service to support
OL,16,Fsurvivors of domestic abuse across
OL,17,Fthree pilot areas throughout the
OL,18,Fcomplex criminal justice process.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@OO]tD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"However, this must be accompanied by
OL,7,Ffunding uplifts for specialist
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse services.
OL,10,F"Robust support for survivors
OL,11,Fnavigating the criminal justice system
OL,12,Fis vital in reducing attrition rates.
OL,13,FHowever, domestic abuse often goes
OL,14,Funseen and unreported, with many cases
OL,15,Fnever reaching the prosecution stage.
OL,17,F"Investment in specialist support
OL,18,Fservices is essential to ensure
OL,19,Fsurvivors can access safety without
OL,20,Fdelay.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"There is a staggering funding gap for
OL,7,Fspecialist services, including refuges
OL,8,Fand community-based services. Until
OL,9,Fthe Government commits to sustainable
OL,10,Ffunding for domestic abuse services,
OL,11,Fwomen and their children will continue
OL,12,Fto pay the price."
OL,14,FDr Jessica Wild, strategic head of
OL,15,Fdomestic abuse at Victim Support said:
OL,16,F"This pilot is welcome news for victim-
OL,17,Fsurvivors whose cases are progressing
OL,18,Fthrough the courts.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"Attending court can be a stressful
OL,7,Fand re-traumatising experience, but
OL,8,Fmeeting the prosecutor beforehand has
OL,9,Freal potential to help
OL,10,Fvictimsurvivors feel more prepared
OL,11,Fand better understand what to expect.
OL,13,F"For these changes to deliver real
OL,14,Fimpact, it is crucial that they are
OL,15,Ftrauma-informed, victim centred and
OL,16,Finclusive of all victim-survivors.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"That requires today's announcement to
OL,7,Fbe backed by specialist training for
OL,8,Fthe CPS, ensuring victims' voices and
OL,9,Fwellbeing are consistently prioritised
OL,10,Fand their needs are properly met.
OL,12,F"We look forward to working closely
OL,13,Fwith the CPS and others to help ensure
OL,14,Fthat victims feel more informed,
OL,15,Fsupported and empowered throughout
OL,16,Ftheir journey through the justice
OL,17,Fsystem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774285870
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FKate Brown, the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService's national lead for domestic
OL,8,Fabuse, said: "For many victims of
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse, the path to justice
OL,10,Fmight feel overwhelming. After such
OL,11,Fisolating and frightening experiences,
OL,12,Fthe criminal justice system must be a
OL,13,Fplace where victims feel supported,
OL,14,Fheard and able to move forward.
OL,16,F"Today's funding announcement shows
OL,17,Fthe real difference support for
OL,18,Fvictims makes. By expanding existing
OL,19,Fpilots, we are making sure more
OL,20,Fdomestic abuse victims feel informed
OL,21,Fand protected at every stage."
OL,26,@pD@NOUxD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
